     {}P.##.F.RmDirByForce targetFolder
     3 ‚éēMKDIR targetFolder
     targetFolder ‚éēNMOVE‚ć†1‚ä£tempFolder,'/*'
     ‚ćě‚Üź'Cider was successfully updated to version ',({1‚Üď‚ćĶ/‚ć®2‚Č§+\‚ćĶ='-'}‚äÉres),' in ',targetFolder,‚éēUCS 10
     ‚ćě‚Üź'The workspace has not been updated, please restart APL.',‚éēUCS 10
